data.description:
Welcome to your new home!  This cozy house is located in the Prescott Country Club subdivision and less than five minutes from the Prescott Golf Club clubhouse.  Nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, step inside to an inviting open kitchen, perfect for both daily living and entertaining. But it doesn't end there - you'll be delighted to find your very own pub right in the backyard, creating a delightful oasis for relaxation and gatherings. 
Additionally, this home offers the unique feature of an Arizona room, providing extra space (approximately 300 sqft) for you to enjoy the beautiful Arizona weather. The Arizona room is not permitted and not included in the listed square footage. 
A brand new 50-year roof will be completed by Christmas!
Don't miss this opportunity. Contact us today!
